""SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM `BoqSalesOrders` AS `p`
INNER JOIN `BoqOrderStatuses` AS `p.tblBoqOrderStatus` ON `p`.`SOStatus_FK` = `p.tblBoqOrderStatus`.`KeyId`
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT `p.Project`.*
    FROM `UserProject` AS `p0`
    INNER JOIN `GNProject` AS `p.Project` ON `p0`.`ProjectId` = `p.Project`.`KeyId`
    WHERE CONVERT(`p0`.`UserID`, CHAR(36)) = @__UserId_0
) AS `t` ON `p`.`ProjectFK` = `t`.`KeyId`
